his book, The Ethics of State Responses to Refugees.

7
00:00:20.139 --> 00:00:22.860
So Doctor Hillier Smith, welcome to the show. It's

8
00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:24.159
a big pleasure to everyone.

9
00:00:25.059 --> 00:00:26.100
Um, THANK you for having me. It's a pleasure

10
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:26.760
to be here.

11
00:00:27.889 --> 00:00:31.129
Uh, SO, let me ask you, uh, before we

12
00:00:31.129 --> 00:00:34.349
get into the actual content of your book. So

